In order to track the production and consumption of IOT device instructions, the message content is such as: `helloABCDEFDCBA`, Kafka is a cluster mode, version 2.5.0

我重写了ChannelInboundHandlerAdapter的channelRead方法，并且添加了`@Trace`注解，得以跟踪TCP消息，代码如下。

I override the channelRead method of ChannelInboundHandlerAdapter and add the @Trace annotation to trace TCP messages. The code is as follows.

```java
    @Trace
    @Override
    public void channelRead(ChannelHandlerContext ctx, Object msg) {
        if (msg instanceof String) {
            String command = (String) msg;
            log.info("channel read message:{}", command);
            ctx.writeAndFlush("\n");
            kafkaService.sendMessageToAdapter(new QueueMessageDTO(instanceId, "xxx", "xxx", "xxx", command));
        }
        ReferenceCountUtil.release(msg);
    }
```

