# Producer

## code

```java
	@Trace
    @Override
    public void channelRead(ChannelHandlerContext ctx, Object msg) {
        if (msg instanceof String) {
            String command = (String) msg;
            ctx.writeAndFlush("\n");
            String uuid = UUID.randomUUID().toString();
            String traceId = TraceContext.traceId();
            TraceContext.putCorrelation("swTraceId", traceId);
            TraceContext.putCorrelation("uuid", uuid);
            log.info("swTraceId:{},uuid:{}, message:{},targetId:{}", traceId, uuid, command, uuid);
            kafkaService.sendMessageToAdapter(new QueueMessageDTO(instanceId, uuid, "one", "one", command));
        }
        ReferenceCountUtil.release(msg);
    }
```

